  "texts": [
    "After filtering down the papers, we divided the papers into two categories.",
    "Papers in first category represent the Explainability for Text Summarization direction in which explainability techniques have been applied to text summarization.",
    "The second category represents the Summarization for Explainability direction and consists of papers where text summarization is used to provide explanations independent of the NLP task under consideration.",
    "The appendix contains definitions of evaluation metrics for text summarization methods (Table 4), example visualizations of explanations from the reviewed papers (Figure 1), and a list of text summarization datasets used (Table 5).",
    "Table 4: Popular metrics for evaluating text summarization."
  ],
